    PROCEDURE: ' Sift together flour, baking powder, and salt; blend in milk and egg; and add gradually to dry ingredients. Stir in corn. Drop from tablespoonful into deep hot fat (365 F.). Cook 2 to 5 minutes; drain on paper towels. ',
