    PROCEDURE: ' Mix carrots, apples, and celery together; stir in pineapple and raisins. Toss all in mayonnaise or dressing; chill. Serve on lettuce cups. If it doesn\'t look fancy enough, slice a banana and top each serving with two or three "silver dollars". Then enjoy a salad like Grandma used to make. ',
