    PROCEDURE: ' Heat pressure cooker and add shortening. Evenly brown meat. Add onion,garlic, and green pepper (+ celery and carrots); brown lightly. Stir in tomatoes, kidney beans, salt, cayenne pepper and chili powder. Place cover on cooker. Cook 15 minutes at COOK position. Remove from heat. Let steam return to stem DOWN position before opening lid. ',
