    PROCEDURE: ' Mix well wafer crumbs, cocoa (if used), 1 cup 4X sugar, nuts, and/or flaked coconut. Add corn syrup, bourbon; mix well. Form into 1" balls. Roll balls in 4X sugar. Store in covered container to ripen. ',
