    PROCEDURE: 'COMBINE all ingredients; beat with fork just until smooth. PLACE well-greased 3 1/2-inch muffin pans or popover pan in a 450 F oven for 3 minutes or until a drop of water sizzles when dropped in them.Removepans from oven; fill them half-full with batter. Bake at 450 F for 15 minutes. Reduce heat to 350 F, bake 20 to 25 additional minutes. Serve immediately. ',
